OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMost areas will be dry with
OL,6,Fsunny spells, especially across
OL,7,Fcentral and southern Britain where it
OL,8,Fwill be very warm. Cloudier and cooler
OL,9,Facross northern Scotland and parts of
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland, with some light rain
OL,11,For drizzle developing at times.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloudy across northern
OL,14,FScotland and parts of Northern Ireland
OL,15,Fwith some light rain or drizzle
OL,16,Fpossible at times. Dry elsewhere, with
OL,17,Fclear spells. A few fog patches
OL,18,Fpossible towards dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
