OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FMost areas remaining dry,
OL,6,Fwith plenty of sunny spells. Cloudier
OL,7,Fin the far north with a few showers
OL,8,Fpossible here. Warm inland but cooler
OL,9,Falong coastal areas.
